data.description:
** Fill out our FREE application now and take the first step towards securing your dream home! **

Welcome to your new home!

This spacious split level home is tucked into a quaint northwestern neighborhood, with easy access to Highway 52 and North Broadway! This 4 bedroom and 2 bath home comes with hard stone counters and black appliances in the kitchen, a large deck overlooking the backyard, and an enormous downstairs living room for all levels of your living comfort! We are adding fresh paint and new vinyl flooring upstairs, with updated light fixtures to make sure this diamond of home shines bright. We have it scheduled to finish fencing the rest of the backyard sometime this spring! Come call this destination your next home!

Pets allowed with approval and pet rent, including big dogs. Fridge, dishwasher stove, washer, and dryer included.

Ability to end lease for free if moving for homeownership, ask us about details! 

Flexible, personalized lease terms, typically with 12 month minimum duration. Resident responsible for all utilities, lawn, and snow.

Proudly managed by Black Swan Living, coupling high quality homes with exceptional customer service. Contact us now to schedule your private tour!

Brokered by Keller Williams Premier Realty-Rochester.
